data.name: Minor Health Potion
data.description: Restores 40HP at the start of the turn if the player has lost more than 50% of his health points.

data.name: Small Antidote
data.description: At the beginning of the turn, if the character has at least one poison on him, removes 20 poison damage.

data.name: Lifesteal Rune
data.description: Restores 10% of the total attack of all elements in HP after a critical strike.

data.name: Burn Rune
data.description: On your first turn, apply a burn effect of 20% of your attack of all elements. The damage is applied each turn and decreases by 10% each time. It is impossible to block.

data.name: Healing Rune
data.description: Every 3 played turns, restores 5% of HP at the start of the turn.
